.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, potato, radish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, alhambra
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, turkish
House: futuristic, art-deco, gothic-revival
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the art-deco house##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the italian##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
6. the gothic-revival house is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Food          | pear      | potato  | radish        |
| Cigar         | alhambra | fonseca | chaman |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | turkish       |
| House           | gothic-revival     | art-deco     | futuristic      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower, daffodil
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, dancer, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bolivar, baccarat
1. the software-developer is the havana-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Flower      | bellflower    | sunflower        | daffodil |
| Job           | dancer    | software-developer | chef    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| Cigar     | baccarat     | havana                | bolivar  |

