.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, poker
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, chaman, prince
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person playing bridge is the prince-smoker##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Game          | whist    | poker  | bridge      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| Cigar   | swisher | chaman    | prince      |

