There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, thai, british
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, superhero
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person watching documentary movies is the thai##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the british is the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the spanish##1
7. the thai is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar         | montecristo | baccarat     | pall-mall   |
| Nationality           | british       | thai   | spanish     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

