.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cherry, spinach
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, subway, car
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, bongani, davidoff
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Food          | asparagus | cherry       | spinach |
| Transport   | car     | bike       | subway   |
| Cigar           | bongani      | fonseca       | davidoff     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

