.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, cherry, plum
City: san-francisco, venice, boston
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, spy
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, soy-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Food          | plum       | cherry         | broccoli   |
| City           | san-francisco | boston | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | mystery        | spy        |
| Beverage   | 7up      | iced-tea           | soy-milk        |

