.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, folk, reggae
City: venice, edinburgh, rome
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, rabbit
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, tram, van
1. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the van##1
3. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person driving the car is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Music-Genre         | folk   | reggae | electronic |
| City   | venice | rome         | edinburgh       |
| Pet           | bird      | rabbit      | fish         |
| Transport     | tram      | van         | car          |

