The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, mechanic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, family, time-travel
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the roller##1
4. the accountant is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the software-developer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Sport       | sailing            | cycling      | volleyball  |
| Job         | software-developer | accountant | mechanic |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy               | time-travel | family |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

