.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, electrician, scientist
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping, board-games
There are 3 different nationalities: british, french, russian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, techno, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the russian##1
6. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | camping | board-games     |
| Nationality   | british   | french       | russian     |
| Music-Genre           | reggae    | techno         | salsa        |

