The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, helicopter
1. the thai is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Flower           | marigold | zinnia | tulip |
| Sport   | rugby        | water-polo       | ice-hockey     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus          | boat      |

