.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, grapes, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, manager, scientist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, tulip
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person eating watermelon is the manager##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the scientist is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Food         | grapes | cabbage | watermelon   |
| Job           | scientist     | chef    | manager   |
| Flower   | poppy         | tulip    | dahlia   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

