.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, water
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, colombian, russian
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, traveling
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, chaman, bolivar
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the russian is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the person drinking water is the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage    | coffee | sprite     | water      |
| Nationality        | dutch | colombian       | russian |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Cigar   | chaman    | pall-mall   | bolivar  |

