.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, traveling
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, indonesian, russian
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the indonesian is the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | almond-milk | cola       |
| Game          | monopoly     | backgammon   | canasta       |
| Hobby         | camping  | traveling   | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | russian       | mexican  |

