.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, russian
House: tower, victorian, art-deco
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk
1. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
5. the art-deco house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | milk    | cola    |
| Nationality          | russian         | spanish    | brazilian   |
| House           | tower | art-deco | victorian |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | d&b     | folk    |

