.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig, mouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, mousecher
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, salsa
There 3 different types of food: tomato, lemon, nectarine
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the mousecher is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person eating tomato##1
4. the fan of reggae is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Pet      | guinea-pig         | mouse     | turtle     |
| Job           | lawyer        | mousecher | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | salsa   | dubstep    |
| Food         | nectarine | tomato   | lemon |

