.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, tram, ship
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, traveling
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, tower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, water-polo
1. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Transport          | ship     | tram    | train    |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | hiking     |
| House   | craftsman  | gothic-revival      | tower        |
| Sport         | handball   | surfing   | water-polo |

 